    {
      "name": "➕ Create Sales Visit",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n    \"customer_id\": 1,\n    \"visit_date\": \"2024-01-15\",\n    \"description\": \"Kunjungan pertama ke customer\",\n    \"activity\": \"Introduction & Product Presentation\",\n    \"activity_weight\": 10,\n    \"status\": \"P\",\n    \"marketing_id\": 1,\n    \"details\": [\n        {\n            \"product_id\": 1,\n            \"quantity\": 10,\n            \"price\": 100000,\n            \"description\": \"Product demo\",\n            \"activity\": \"Product presentation\",\n            \"activity_weight\": 5,\n            \"progress\": \"0\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"product_id\": 2,\n            \"quantity\": 5,\n            \"price\": 250000,\n            \"description\": \"Secondary product\",\n            \"activity\": \"Product discussion\",\n            \"activity_weight\": 3,\n            \"progress\": \"0\"\n        }\n    ]\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/sales/sales-visits",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["sales", "sales-visits"]
        },
        "description": "Create a new sales visit with details.\n\n**Required Fields:**\n- `customer_id`: ID of the customer\n- `visit_date`: Visit date in format YYYY-MM-DD\n- `marketing_id`: User ID of the marketing/sales person\n- `details`: Array of visit details (cannot be empty)\n  - `product_id`: Product ID (required)\n  - `quantity`: Quantity (required, must be > 0)\n  - `price`: Price per unit (required, must be >= 0)\n  - `progress`: Progress stage (required)\n\n**Optional Fields:**\n- `description`: Visit description\n- `activity`: Activity name\n- `activity_weight`: Activity weight (default: 0)\n- `status`: Visit status - `P` (Plan), `F` (Finish), `C` (Cancel). Default: `P`\n- Detail fields: `description`, `activity`, `activity_weight`\n\n**Progress Values:**\n- `0` - Plan\n- `1` - Visit\n- `2` - Opportunity\n- `3` - Trial\n- `4` - Quotation\n- `5` - Negotiation\n- `6` - PO (Purchase Order/Deal)\n- `C` - Cancel\n- `P` - Pending"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success Response (200 OK)",
          "originalRequest": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/sales/sales-visits"
          },
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
          "body": "{\n    \"data\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"code\": \"VIS-20240115-0001\",\n        \"customer\": {\n            \"id\": 1,\n            \"name\": \"Customer Name\",\n            \"code\": \"CUST-001\"\n        },\n        \"visit_date\": \"2024-01-15\",\n        \"description\": \"Kunjungan pertama ke customer\",\n        \"activity\": \"Introduction & Product Presentation\",\n        \"activity_weight\": 10,\n        \"status\": \"P\",\n        \"marketing\": {\n            \"id\": 1,\n            \"name\": \"Marketing Name\",\n            \"username\": \"marketing1\",\n            \"photo_profile\": \"\",\n            \"avatar_url\": \"\"\n        },\n        \"details\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": 1,\n                \"visit_id\": 1,\n                \"product\": {\n                    \"id\": 1,\n                    \"name\": \"Product Name\",\n                    \"code\": \"PRD-001\"\n                },\n                \"quantity\": 10,\n                \"price\": 100000,\n                \"description\": \"Product demo\",\n                \"activity\": \"Product presentation\",\n                \"activity_weight\": 5,\n                \"progress\": \"0\",\n                \"before_progress\": \"0\",\n                \"total_value\": 1000000\n            }\n        ],\n        \"created_at\": \"2024-01-15T10:00:00Z\",\n        \"updated_at\": \"2024-01-15T10:00:00Z\"\n    }\n}"
        },
        {
          "name": "Error Response (400 Bad Request)",
